  <description><![CDATA[<p>The superb ski-inclusive hotel has everything that you need for a week’s skiing included in the holiday price; a 6 day lift pass, skis or snowboard and boots, full board including wine, children’s clubs, evening entertainment and much more (see Inghams Plus). Located on the edge of the forest by the Cheval Noir piste, access to the slopes is quick and easy and the resort centre is only a 5 minute walk away.</p>
<p><strong>Families</strong>: Mini Clubs for children including Câlins (3mths-2yrs) and Malins (3-5yrs), open Sunday-Friday from 8.30am-6pm and 7pm-9pm with a full programme of indoor and outdoor activities. Malins also includes lessons in the Jardin de Neiges. Children dine with the activity leader for lunch and parents in the evenings. Children’s club Copains (6-10yrs) is open afternoons all season and full days 21 Dec-3 Jan and 15 Feb-14 Mar. The Club Jeune (11-17yrs) is open full days 21 Dec-3 Jan, 15 Feb-14 Mar and 5-11 Apr. It includes pick up and drop off to ski school meeting place if required (lessons not included).</p>]]></description>
